          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Fast-track incorporation combined with direct commercial tax pipelines to bypass traditional queues.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Block 3: Offices Suite -->
      <div class="relative bg-white border border-slate-200/60 p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-slate-300 hover:shadow-md overflow-hidden group bg-white">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-[4px] bg-[#004B23] transition-all duration-300 group-hover:w-[6px]"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-1.5">
